vote.title: Authorize acquisition from Sunstone Group, Inc., of approximately 72,032 square feet of commercially improved land located in Collin County for the COVID-19 Supportive Housing Project. - Not to exceed $6,630,000.00 ($6,600,000.00, plus closing costs and title expenses not to exceed $30,000.00) - Financing: U.S. Department of Treasury - Coronavirus Relief Funds
